 Production: $29-134/month depending on traffic ROI Timeline: Launch MVP in 2-4 weeks, breakeven at 50-100 users #2 RUNNER-UP: WeWeb ⭐⭐⭐⭐½ Best for: Professional developers who want frontend flexibility + backend freedom Click-by-Click Implementation SOP: Step\tAction\tWhere to Click\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tRationale/Notes 1\tCreate account\tweweb.io → \"Start for free\"\tEmail credentials\tEditor access\tFree development environment 2\tChoose template\tDashboard → \"New project\" → Browse templates\tSelect starting template\tPre-built structure\t100+ templates available 3\tConnect backend\tIntegrations → \"Add data source\"\tChoose Supabase/Airtable/Firebase\tDatabase connected\tNo vendor lock-in 4\tDesign pages\tVisual editor → Drag components\tPlace elements, bind data\tDynamic page created\tFull responsive control 5\tAdd workflows\tElement → \"Add action\"\tOn-click, on-load events\tInteractive behaviors\tJavaScript-like logic 6\tIntegrate AI\tOpenAI plugin OR custom API\tAPI keys + prompts\tAI features embedded\tNative OpenAI integration 7\tSet up auth\tAuth plugin → Configure\tAuthentication provider (Auth0, Supabase)\tLogin system active\tFlexible auth options 8\tCustom code\tSettings → Custom code section\tInsert JS/CSS\tEnhanced functionality\tFull code access 9\tDeploy\tTop-right → \"Publish\"\tChoose hosting tier\tLive URL generated\t$49/month for production 10\tConnect domain\tSettings → Domains\tAdd CNAME records\tCustom domain live\tSSL included COST BREAKDOWN: Development: $0/month Production: $49/month (Starter) or $99/month (Pro) Unique Advantage: Use ANY backend (Postgres, MongoDB, etc.) #3 SPECIALIZED: Retool ⭐⭐⭐⭐ Best for: Internal tools, admin dashboards, data management interfaces Click-by-Click Implementation SOP: Step\tAction\tWhere to Click\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tRationale/Notes 1\tSign up\tretool.com → \"Get started\"\tCompany email\tFree account (5 users)\tGenerous free tier 2\tCreate app\t\"Create new\" → \"App\"\tApp